<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <title>Question reply notification</title>
    <style>
        .name{
            font-size: 2rem;
            font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
            font-weight: 600;

        }
        .name span {
            font-weight: bold;
            color: rgb(33, 225, 33);
        }

        p{
            font-size: 1.4rem;
            font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1;

        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <h1 class="name">Hello <span> <%= name %> </span></h1>
    <p>A new reply has been added to your question in the video <span>><%=title %></span></p>
    <p>Please login to our website to view the reply and continue the discussion</p>
    <p>Thank you for being a part of our community!</p>
</body>
</html>